     FFmpeg 2.4 includes the following library versions:

       â€¢ libavutil      54.7.100
       â€¢ libavcodec     56.1.100
       â€¢ libavformat    56.4.101
       â€¢ libavdevice    56.0.100
       â€¢ libavfilter     5.1.100
       â€¢ libswscale      3.0.100
       â€¢ libswresample   1.1.100
       â€¢ libpostproc    53.0.100

     Important API changes since 2.3:

       â€¢ The new field mime_type was added to AVProbeData, which can
         cause crashes, if it is not initialized.
       â€¢ Some deprecated functions were removed.
       â€¢ The avfilter_graph_parse function was made compatible with Libav.
       â€¢ The Matroska demuxer now outputs verbatim ASS packets.

     Please refer to the doc/APIchanges file for more information.

